What changes would most improve the corporate culture at your job??? Most upper management is appointed, if not anointed for the positions they hold. I left my job. Executive staff worried more about themselves and their futures rather than the future of the organization. People with skill and ability were fired, demoted or had their pay frozen for years. Morale sank. People left. The executives then replaced skilled and experienced workers with consultants or contractors. Institutional memory was lost. The needs of customer were forgotten. Ridiculous rules, including union rules made working impossible. Technology was seen as the savior and panacea for all organizational ills and was instituted without fully understanding business processes or the limitations of technology. More money was spent upgrading unneeded technology rather than focusing on people who know how to work. Executives were very well compensated while middle management was decimated and reduced in pay grades. Training and testing of employees for promotion was forgotten. Customers became an obstruction. Travel between business divisions was restricted and personal contacts were lost. The human factors of doing business were ended. I would fire and replace the executive staff from the CEO on down. I would fire all the consultants. I would institute new training and promotions based upon testing and performance, real results to improve moral. I would pay back all employees who lost pay because of the wage freezes. I would reduct the dependency upon unneeded and unwanted technology and replace it wherever possible with humans. I would restore customer confidence and would seek the input of our customers to see what we must do to keep them satisfied. I would also sue and claw back every dollar charged by consultants and contractors who did no work other than jam up the paper copiers and the shredders. I would recruit, fresh new college and high school students and working moms who need jobs and even provide day care for their kids. And for single dads too! I would change the entire culture of the organization and do it quickly and efficiently while gaining the trust and respect of customers and business associates. It's hard work but it can be done. I would have done that.
